Packages 
Package Description
Attributes
This package includes classes describing the different attributes of the various objects/keys.
ClientInterfaces
This package encompasses all classes required for successful interfacing of operations to be used by the user.
Enum
This package encompasses classes mapping the various types of operations, result statuses, tags, types and objects to their subsequent tags as specified by KMIP for TTLV encoding.
Keys
This encompasses the POJO classes of the keys supported by the library.
KMIPTypes
This package encompasses POJO classes describing various data types as interpreted by KMIP protocol for reading values.
Messages
This package encompasses classes describing various parts of Request and Response Messages as well as classes describing Request and Response Messages as a whole.
Objects
This encompasses classes which have information/properties about various objects.
Operations
This package encompasses classes that facilitate working with the response message received from the server.
